  "blurb": "A contemporary beachfront villa set directly on the white sand of Chaweng — five en-suite bedrooms, a 17-metre pool with a sunken sala, and a private cinema, gym, spa and kids' club, with an open-plan living core framing the Gulf. Move-in ready, freehold.",
  "detail": "Positioned directly on the white sands of the prestigious Chaweng Palm area, this beachfront villa blends contemporary architecture with timeless island luxury across a 1,200 m² plot and 820 m² of refined living space. Five en-suite bedrooms deliver privacy and calm, while expansive open-plan living and dining areas and a seamless indoor-outdoor flow maximize ocean views — equally suited to a private residence or a high-return investment.\n\nThe outdoor space centres on a 17-metre swimming pool with a sunken pool sala, a shaded retreat that frames the sea, alongside a tropical garden, sunbeds and an outdoor BBQ and dining area. Inside, the villa is delivered with a full suite of premium facilities: a private cinema, a fully equipped gym, a dedicated spa, a kids' club, a gourmet kitchen and secure parking, all finished to a high standard.\n\nDespite its exclusive, gated setting, the villa sits in the heart of Chaweng — steps from the island's best restaurants, shopping and nightlife, with Samui International Airport just fifteen minutes away. Offered freehold and turnkey, it is a rare move-in-ready beachfront asset in one of Thailand's most coveted destinations.",
